  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Ok, I get it. `helper.state` is the current state of the helper, `state` is the state if was before sending the `search`. In practice, we'll only need the `state`, and even this one we'll not need that often.\n",
    "created_at": "2015-09-14T12:35:27Z",
